{
  "id": "class_0058",
  "name": "Banished Royal Herald",
  "title_completion": "a Banished Royal Herald",
  "flavor_text": "Once your voice carried the weight of crowns, your proclamations scattering lesser men like leaves before a gale. Now the Mad King's Exile Writ bears your own name, and you have learned that a herald without a throne commands something far more dangerous than loyalty \u2014 the wind itself remembers every word you ever spoke. You wander the marble corridors of memory, unrolling decrees that bleed into the air and swallow armies whole.",
